html_attributions: 一虎拉麵 灣仔 Ichitora Ramen at Wanchai

reviews.text: Great ramen and huge portions. There was a queue when I came (Sunday night) but it was very well organized and moved along swiftly. The place is very small and charming, much recommended.
This is always going to be my favourite ramen please. Reasonably price , taste yum. Fast service. Good portion size.
Five stars for the summer Lemon Ramen. Also liked the original one, but the lemon one is something special.
I love ramen, delicious!
Their seasonal lemon ramen during the summer is the absolute must try. I come annually just for it!

result.name: 一虎拉麵

html_attributions: 一虎拉麵 灣仔 Ichitora Ramen at Wanchai

reviews.text: Great ramen and huge portions. There was a queue when I came (Sunday night) but it was very well organized and moved along swiftly. The place is very small and charming, much recommended.
湯個味道唔算重，唔似一般豚骨果種膠質既口感，飲完亦都唔會口乾。拉麵似一蘭/豚王，有辣椒醬係上面。叉燒無肥膏，辣芽菜亦好好食。如果覺得豚王既湯太濃，可以試下呢間。

檸檬拉麵大推
好啱夏天食
解決左天氣熱怕肥膩唔想食拉麵既問題
怕酸既人我建議早啲夾走幾片檸檬，唔係食到尾會太酸
This is always going to be my favourite ramen please. Reasonably price , taste yum. Fast service. Good portion size.
非常好味值得一試
